java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.client.model.generators.CustomLoaderBuilder<T>
net.minecraftforge.client.model.generators.loaders.DynamicFluidContainerModelBuilder<T>
public class DynamicFluidContainerModelBuilder<T extends ModelBuilder<T>> extends CustomLoaderBuilder<T>
已过时。
Use Vanilla's providers ModelProvider
In 1.21.4 Mojang exposed their data generators for their models. So it should be feasible to just use theirs. If you find something lacking feel free to open a PR so that we can extend it.
